snippet.title: Daemonologie Trailer June 2024
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3048140/Daemonologie/

Daemonologie is an upcoming Scottish folk horror tale based on the 17th century witch trials. 
You play the part of a witch finder and must sort truth from lies. On the 5th day a witch must hang. Best you know who by then.
